{"tid":577240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[華春瑩上線勒]澳教授新書批北京滲透　華春瑩引李白詩句反駁","createTime":"2018-03-01T14:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T09:29:23.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6566a9b580c5fa2f480f30f04144fb710a3fe36b","tid":577240,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180301/s00004/1519914237471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180301%2Fs00004%2F1519914237471&d=9VV33zXz2pnOT0pVERM40MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a3883ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180301%2Fs00004%2F1519914237471&h=a4bb4bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180301/s00004/1519914237471</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180301/s00004/d363ebd3e46680e6562a797c502d9139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180301%2Fs00004%2Fd363ebd3e46680e6562a797c502d9139.jpg&h=583385c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲學者漢密爾頓（Clive Hamilton）周一（2月26日）出版新書，講述中國政府如何影響與滲透澳洲，以及中國人大規模移居澳洲現象，消息一出惹起中澳兩國輿論熱議。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩在例行記者會上被問及有關風波時，引用唐朝詩人李白詩句，批有關書籍是惡意炒作及抹黑攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩引用詩句是「兩岸猿聲啼不住，輕舟已過萬重山」，出自李白七言絕詩《早發白帝城》。華春瑩稱，漢密爾頓新書是惡意炒作和抹黑攻擊，顯得毫無意義價值。<br />\n<br />\n漢密爾頓來自坎培拉查爾斯史都華大學，專攻公共倫理學。新書〈Silent Invasion: How China is Turning Australia into a Puppet State〉（沉默入侵：中國如何令澳洲變成傀儡國家；暫譯），原定今年4月出版，但出版社表示基於「全面法律意見」，決定延後出版。<br />\n<br />\n外界質疑有關決定屬自我審查，亦有聲音批評出版社懼怕北京指控誹謗。爭議聲下，出版社最後決定提前新書在周一出版。<br />\n<br />\n早前有傳聞指華春瑩因家中私藏大筆美金被捕，以致今日甫一出場，引起部分在場記者驚呼。她則以微笑應對，神色泰然。"},{"pid":"0e7128456444027776dfdd1079b63b94e1510eaf","tid":577240,"uid":550,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"兩岸猿聲啼不住，輕舟已過萬重山<br />\n係咪即係話而家先知已經太遲"},{"pid":"7898710c82d48c73fa1dffabf59aa5fd15064c66","tid":577240,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"條八婆傾掂數?"},{"pid":"47ee9afeb05124b0448783b77640b9d1d67d889a","tid":577240,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7128456444027776dfdd1079b63b94e1510eaf","tid":577240,"uid":550,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"兩岸猿聲啼不住，輕舟已過萬重山<br />\n係咪即係話而家先知已經太遲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話hamilton你講黎都嘥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3c58a13ed23ed4ef98536277e08ad4f6831518","tid":577240,"uid":39872,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"引用唐詩，真唔知醜<br />\n用蝗語你可以讀到押韻咩"},{"pid":"1c5f7226c23bfc5798d72bcf085d93df1f907a99","tid":577240,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"吊，冇戲睇"},{"pid":"35a01522a4d0391a09c9a11600d5be88f23e7a9e","tid":577240,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"充公全部美金 所以放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8766017f6a0f0cac4ee7c632cd635e620ddff3","tid":577240,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"47ee9afeb05124b0448783b77640b9d1d67d889a","tid":577240,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7128456444027776dfdd1079b63b94e1510eaf","tid":577240,"uid":550,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"兩岸猿聲啼不住，輕舟已過萬重山<br />\n係咪即係話而家先知已經太遲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h